<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }
    .code-box {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .code-box .code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #667eea;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    .code-box p {
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: #856404;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888888;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome to MedChain, {{userName}}!</h2>
      <p>Thank you for signing up. To get started, please verify your email address by entering the code below or clicking the verification link.</p>

      <div class="code-box">
        <p>Verification Code:</p>
        <div class="code">{{verificationCode}}</div>
        <p>This code expires in 24 hours</p>
      </div>

      <p>Or click the button below to verify directly:</p>
      <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="cta-button">Verify Email Address</a>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>Security Notice:</strong> If you did not sign up for a MedChain account, please disregard this email. Do not share this verification code with anyone.
      </div>

      <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      <a href="{{verificationLink}}">{{verificationLink}}</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2024 MedChain. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="{{termsUrl}}">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
